Who Am I?

Hello! My name is Jennifer Cao and I am currently a senior at the University of Pittsburgh studying Computer Science + Digital Narrative and Interactive Design (DNID). I mostly focused on back-end developnebt, though my affinty towards design does draw me towards front-end development as well. As someone who does particularly love narrative-based games, I have also dabbled in game design, particularly on the storytelling side. I am originally from New Jersey in the New York Metropolitan Area. Outside of computer science related areas, I enjoy art, music, travelling, and good food (a live-to- eat type of person, ifyou will). { }
